channel.title: Pointless Celebrities
channel.desc: A special Comedy edition of the general knowledge quiz in which four teams try to come up with the answers that no-one else could think of. Presented by Alexander Armstrong and co-host Richard Osman, and featuring Geoff Norcott, Danny John-Jules, Ninia Benjamin, Ed Byrne, Olivia Lee, Kerry Howard, Clair Buckley and James Buckley.
